      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "• Bloomberg B-PIPE / API\n  - Real-time price, 52W range\n  - Consensus estimates (EPS, Rev)\n  - Analyst ratings & targets\n  - Peer comparison (5-10 comps)\n  - Institutional ownership\n  - Short interest, ESG scores\n  - M&A history, credit ratings\n• FactSet (alternative)\n  - Similar coverage, slightly cheaper\n• Refinitiv (LSEG)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• Bloomberg B-PIPE / API\n  - Real-time price, 52W range\n  - Consensus estimates (EPS, Rev)\n  - Analyst ratings & targets\n  - Peer comparison (5-10 comps)\n  - Institutional ownership\n  - Short interest, ESG scores\n  - M&A history, credit ratings\n• FactSet (alternative)\n  - Similar coverage, slightly cheaper\n• Refinitiv (LSEG)",
      "lineHeight": 1.3,
